  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;enchantment&nbsp;(compulsion)&nbsp;[mind-affecting];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;bard 4, mesmerist 4, psychic 4, sorcerer/wizard 4, witch 4;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 round<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (a few drops of river water)<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;close (25 ft. + 5 ft./2 levels)<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;one living creature<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 minute/level<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will negates;&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell acts as the <i>deeper slumber</i> spell, but only affects one creature of 10 Hit Dice or fewer. In addition, a creature affected by this spell awakens with no knowledge of the events that led to the spell's casting. The target loses all memory from the 5 minutes prior to falling asleep. No effect short of a <i>miracle</i> or <i>wish</i> can restore memories lost by this spell.</p>\n</div>\n",
